name: ☆ sleeping ✧˖° ☽
description: falling asleep, consciousness fading away into undefinable places, muscles slowly getting heavier, blurry first dreams are starting to shape out, and 💥/SUDDENLY!/💥 some exterior, far coming, maybe not even real unwelcomed noise, or an unfortunate cliff falling vision that creeped out in that early dream, takes it all away at once.
